          />
        </div>
        <div class="col-xl-4 col-lg-5">
          <div class="featured-text text-center text-lg-left">
            <h4>Digital Branding</h4>
            <p class="text-black-50 mb-0">
              Digital branding include: defining a core brand idea, customer
              experience data analysis, company and product unique identity
              development, creative development, digital visualization and
              content development, digital brand standards and guides
              development, experimenting and implementation.
            </p>
