        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <div class="bg-white text-center h-100 project">
            <div class="d-flex h-100">
              <div class="project-text w-100 my-auto text-center text-lg-left">
                <h4 class="text-black">Digital Communications</h4>
                <p class="mb-0 text-black-50">
                  Digital communications include: content strategy development,
                  visualization, SMM, SEO/SEM, paid and display advertising,
                  email campaigns, influencer marketing, mobile communications,
